    <title>在ArchLinux上安装Steam并运行拳皇13</title>
    <link>https://wjinlei.github.io/archlinux_steam/</link>
    <pubDate>Mon, 15 May 2023 12:24:13 &#43;0800</pubDate><author>
                        <name>无所谓王同学</name><uri>https://github.com/Wjinlei</uri><email>wjinlei.1996@qq.com</email></author><guid>https://wjinlei.github.io/archlinux_steam/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/archlinux_steam/05.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>得益于<code>Proton</code>技术的支持，让我们可以运行<code>Steam</code>上的大部分游戏。<br>
下面我就以<code>拳皇13</code>为例子来演示<code>ArchLinux</code>下安装<code>Steam</code>，快来一起看看吧！</p>
</blockquote>]]></description>
</item><item>
    <title>在ArchLinux上安装MAME模拟器并运行拳皇97</title>
    <link>https://wjinlei.github.io/archlinux_kof/</link>
    <pubDate>Sat, 02 Jul 2022 16:34:20 &#43;0800</pubDate><author>
                        <name>无所谓王同学</name><uri>https://github.com/Wjinlei</uri><email>wjinlei.1996@qq.com</email></author><guid>https://wjinlei.github.io/archlinux_kof/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/archlinux_kof/running01.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>事情的起因是这样的，我最近买了一台街机摇杆<code>拳霸Q4</code>，安奈不住激动的心情，马上就装了个<code>虚拟机</code>。<br>
然后通过虚拟机运行模拟器，再把USB接到虚拟机里来玩，但我发现，游戏总是玩不了多久就很卡。</p>
</blockquote>]]></description>
